## Key Conventions

- UseCases handle one operation each.
- Repositories are interfaces in Application/Domain, implemented in Infrastructure.
- Events and Listeners belong to Infrastructure or Application.
- Jobs and Queues belong to Infrastructure.
- No Eloquent in Domain or Application layers.
- No HTTP types (Request, Response) in Domain or Application layers.
